<D>__{the yellow one.}
<C>__{jenny}
<D>__{oh, wow... i will tell you what. when the baby is born, we'll go out in my back yard and wave to you.}
<C>__{star man}
<P>__{(smiles)}
<D>__{i will wave to you.}
<A>__{all we can hear are the tires humming over the road. the camaro rounds the side of a low hill.}
<C>__{star man}
<D>__{oh, shit!}
<A>__{jenny slams on the brakes. one of the cobra helicopters, lit from the inside, is parked next to a line of flares across the road ahead.}
